    "body" : "<p>I would use a regex.</p>\n\n<pre><code>String text = \"-jaskdh2367sd.27askjdfh23\";\nString digits = text.replaceAll(\"[^0-9.]\", \"\");\nSystem.out.println(digits);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>prints</p>\n\n<pre><code>2367.2723\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You might like to keep <code>-</code> as well for negative numbers.</p>\n"
