    "body" : "<p>With guava:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String input = \"abx123.5\";\nString result = CharMatcher.inRange('0', '9').or(CharMatcher.is('.')).retainFrom(input);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>see <a href=\"http://code.google.com/p/guava-libraries/wiki/StringsExplained\">http://code.google.com/p/guava-libraries/wiki/StringsExplained</a></p>\n"
