    "body" : "<h1>Solution</h1>\n<h2>With dash</h2>\n<pre><code>String phoneNumberstr = &quot;Tel: 00971-557890-999&quot;;\nString numberRefined = phoneNumberstr.replaceAll(&quot;[^\\\\d-]&quot;, &quot;&quot;);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Result: <code>0097-557890-999</code>.</p>\n<h2>Without dash</h2>\n<p>If you also do not need &quot;-&quot; in String you can do like this:</p>\n<pre><code>String phoneNumberstr = &quot;Tel: 00971-55 7890 999&quot;;      \nString numberRefined = phoneNumberstr.replaceAll(&quot;[^0-9]&quot;, &quot;&quot;);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Result: <code>0097557890999</code>.</p>\n"
  }, {
