      "body" : "Since the <code>StringBuffer</code> is only being used inside the function, and not shared between threads, it would be recommended, for performance reasons, to use <code>StringBuilder</code>, instead. See: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/4793503/679240\">stackoverflow.com/a/4793503/679240</a> and <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/2771852/679240\">stackoverflow.com/a/2771852/679240</a>"
    } ],
