    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This handles null inputs, negative numbers and decimals (you need to include the Apache Commons Lang library, version 3.8 or higher, in your project):</p>\n\n<pre><code>import org.apache.commons.lang3.RegExUtils;\nresult = RegExUtils.removeAll(input, \"-?[^\\\\d.]\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Library reference: <a href=\"https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/apidocs/org/apache/commons/lang3/RegExUtils.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/apidocs/org/apache/commons/lang3/RegExUtils.html</a></p>\n"
